ubrd header file description:
ubrd_config.h define global struct and MACRO for ubrd;
init.preload.eng.rc config libudf.so LD_PRELOAD mechanism, only enable it on eng load;


libudf.so: 
user space debug framework library which includes MTK memory/fdleak/ubrd debug feature, 
it load through LD_PRELOAD mechanism, and rehook libc system call for add intermediate debug;


Terminology:
udf - user space debug framework
ubrd - user space backtrace record

